    },
    {
      "start": 429.2,
      "end": 430.46,
      "text": "emotional"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.46,
      "end": 434.62,
      "text": "그리고 원망과 슬픔이 가득 찬 그런 표정이었거든요"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.62,
      "end": 435.34,
      "text": "yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 435.34,
      "end": 438.8,
      "text": "he blames his dad for Percival's death I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.8,
      "end": 440.0,
      "text": "it's your fault"
    },
    {
      "start": 440.0,
      "end": 441.04,
      "text": "그런 것 같아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.04,
      "end": 442.04,
      "text": "you made me leave"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.04,
      "end": 442.06,
      "text": "you made me leave"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.06,
      "end": 442.56,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.56,
      "end": 444.56,
      "text": "그런데 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 444.56,
